<div class="title">Infant Gnostics of Platonic Love</div>
<div class="substance">5-MeO-DMT</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Staraflur&Exact=1">Staraflur</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Staraflur. "Infant Gnostics of Platonic Love: An Experience with 5-MeO-DMT (exp4752)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Jan 1, 2002. erowid.org/exp/4752</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
<table cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" align="right" border="0">
